The Ocean's Deadliest New Species | 5-Headed Shark Attack | Full Monster Action Movie

The beautiful island is home to thousands of species of aquatic life. Now, there is a new species: the 5-Headed Shark is all heads and teeth. Shaped like a demented starfish, this monster terrorizes the open ocean before invading the beaches of Puerto Rico, endangering the once peaceful island paradise.

2017.  Stars: Chris Bruno, Nikki Howard, Lindsay Sawyer
